Package dimstyl.orm.internal.sql.resolver

package dimstyl.orm.internal.sql.resolver
Contains classes for resolving database column types.
  • Class
    Description
    ColumnTypeResolver
    Interface for resolving SQL column types based on Java field types.
    ColumnTypeResolverFactory
    Factory class for obtaining the appropriate ColumnTypeResolver instance based on the specified DatabaseEngine.
    DerbyColumnTypeResolver
    Singleton enum implementation of ColumnTypeResolver for Apache Derby.
    H2ColumnTypeResolver
    Singleton enum implementation of ColumnTypeResolver for the H2 database.
    SQLiteColumnTypeResolver
    Singleton enum implementation of ColumnTypeResolver for the SQLite database.
